{"title":"碗的叠放","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2463","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小 H有 n 个碗需要放进橱柜，她希望将他们叠起来放置。你知道每个碗都是规则的圆柱体，并且都是上宽下窄，你已经测量出了每个碗的两个半径及高，请你帮小H找出一种叠放顺序，使得叠放出来的碗堆的高度尽量小。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个整数 n，表示碗的数目。以下n 行，每行三个整数h，r1，r2。分别表示碗高及两个半径。其中 r1&lt;r2。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仅一个数，表示最小的高度。答案四舍五入取整。&nbsp;</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3 <br>50 30 80 <br>35 25 70 <br>40 10 90</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>55 </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>100%数据满足 n&lt;=9。所有输入的数绝对值不超过 1000。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}